headline: Evaluating Generac Holdings (GNRC) Valuation After Recent Share Price Swings
summary: Generac Holdings (GNRC) is back in focus after recent share price swings, with the stock moving higher over the past week but showing weaker returns over the past month and past 3 months. See our latest analysis for Generac Holdings. Zooming out, Generac’s recent bounce comes after a 30 day share price return of 8.28% decline and a 90 day share price return of 10.17% decline, while the 1 year total shareholder return of 2.96% decline contrasts with a 3 year total shareholder return of 34.42%...
